metadata.title: Trans-Alaska Pipeline
metadata.description: Data Type: Infrastructure;   The route of the Trans-Alaska Pipeline was received from Alyeska Pipeline Service Company via the State Pipeline Coordinator's Office. Written permission to include these data as part of the DNR digital basemap has been received from the Alyeska Pipeline Service Company.
